Ghana Says Hedged Crude Oil Sales at $107 a Barrel For May to December

-- B y   M o s e s   M o z a r t   D z a w u
-- 
2011-06-09T11:57:55Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-09/ghana-says-hedged-crude-oil-sales-at-107-a-barrel-for-may-to-december.html
Ghana  has hedged its crude sales at
$107 per barrel from May to December, Kwame Okyere-Mensuo, a
technical advisor at the Ministry of Finance and  Economic
Planning , told reporters today in the capital, Accra.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Moses Mozart Dzawu in Accra at 
